},{"pid":"775aaef5b0e6be0cbeb2e07cec0f9c6389e97e48","tid":199714,"uid":60261,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T15:06:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Retake DSE仲易入啦</blockquote><br />\n我15 DSE嫁...無得combine cert<br />\n我唔肯定考唔考得返之前個分</blockquote><br />\n點會冇得combine cert<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dedd93cbf856aa3fa596bbfc4210177391c6e5d2","tid":199714,"uid":69422,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T16:26:27.000Z","msg":"Asso/HD year 1 non jupas 上返 CU Engine 唔清楚<br />\n<br />\n如果你想year 2 升返 CU CS year 3 <br />\n你預自己year 2 sem 1 cgpa &gt;3.7先大機會有first round interview<br />\n如果係ive應該要cgpa &gt; 3.85<br />\nN手飯唔清楚會派到幾多cgpa<br />\n<br />\n我自己interview嗰時就見到<br />\n1個space HD IT cgpa ~3.7x<br />\n1個IVE software Engineering cgpa ~3.9x<br />\n我覺得應該無話邊間會著數啲<br />\n<br />\n另外我估佢哋會睇埋DSE成績<br />\n首先留意返CU non jupas 只會收full cert / 補返IELTS, GCSE, IGCSE etc.<br />\n我自己hkcc cgpa 3.8X, DSE full cert best 5 ~20有interview<br />\n但係我cgpa高過我既同學反而無"},{"pid":"962e3570d187ac8a9ad72b9a5c65128212a5be3b","tid":199714,"uid":58327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T17:29:03.000Z","msg":"巴打有人做何必要做狗呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0e109c7fe4f72380fc1eaec1a24aafec8b9f649","tid":199714,"uid":43720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T17:43:28.000Z","msg":"Cuscs啦<br />\nCu親生仔"},{"pid":"6fbc8875c15cf3ee90281f9f3ae44090c7ef0ab0","tid":199714,"uid":69422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T18:43:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Cuscs啦<br />\nCu親生仔</blockquote><br />\ncuscs 好伏喎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c43a6a199f778529e66d23abaff39d9c1b8fefac","tid":199714,"uid":33631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T03:38:14.000Z","msg":"cu engine收咁撚低都唔夠分入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\"